/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date				Who		Reason
10 February 2021	navmd1	Initial creation TFS 49052 MACS3 Vessel Library API

*/

vars

begin
	return self.deck = self.JSONOnDeck;
epilog

end;</source>
        <ReturnType type="Boolean"/>
    </JadeMethod>
